title.narrative: Development Policies for the State of Sergipe

description.narrative: The Development Policy Objective of the proposed operation is to improve public sector management, and expand access to quality public services and economic opportunities for the extremely poor in the State of Sergipe. The proposed operation is fully consistentwith the overarching objective of the CPS 2012-2015, and with the strategic objectives of enhancing the efficiency of public investments, improving quality and expand provision of public services, and promoting regional economic development. It is also fully aligned with the Government of Sergipe's goal to eradicate poverty, as outlined in the Multiyear Participatory Plan (PPA-P) 2012-2015.
